item.title: Engineering UPO Finals Week, Student Support Program
item.description: Engineering student appreciation and final exam study snacks!  Meet Engineering partners, liaisons and representatives.  Learn about Engineering, campus and community resources.  Pick up Finals Week study snacks, academic resources, coupons and much more!  Sponsored by the College of Engineering CARE, WIE, MEP, IEFX, ECS & Engineering International Student Programs!
